{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"QuickStart","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"YEOFR"}]},"abstract":[{"text":"Recognise the enrolled user and reject everyone else, in a few lines.","type":"text"}],"kind":"article","seeAlsoSections":[{"anchor":"Getting-started","identifiers":["doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService"],"generated":true,"title":"Getting started"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/QuickStart"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/quickstart"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/yeofr\/quickstart"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"1. Add the SDK","anchor":"1-Add-the-SDK","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Add the ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YEOFR"}]},{"type":"text","text":" Swift package"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"https:\/\/github.com\/YEOMessaging\/YEOFR-SPM"},{"text":") to your project, then","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"import YEOFR"},{"type":"text","text":". The binary is "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"arm64 device-only","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" — it does not run on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the simulator.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"2. Pilot unlock for non-YEO bundle IDs","anchor":"2-Pilot-unlock-for-non-YEO-bundle-IDs","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"YEOFR is gated to YEO-owned apps by default; a non-YEO bundle id aborts on"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"construction. Evaluation customers get a ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"temporary unlock code"}]},{"text":" that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"bypasses the gate during a fixed pilot window — email","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"christo@yeomessaging.com"}]},{"text":" to request one. Pass it to the initializer","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"(step 3). If your app’s bundle id is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"com.youreyeonly.*"},{"text":", the gate passes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"natively.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","text":"3. Drive everything with `FaceTrustService`","anchor":"3-Drive-everything-with-FaceTrustService","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService","isActive":true},{"text":" is the turnkey entry point. It owns the engine, the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"camera, the fused-trust pipeline (face recognition + liveness CNN +","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TrueDepth), the identity gate, and tracker persistence, and exposes two","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"streams: one for live trust verdicts and one for guided enrolment.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["import YEOFR","","let service = FaceTrustService(pilotUnlockCode: \"YOUR-PILOT-CODE\")","","\/\/ Attach the preview to an AVCaptureVideoPreviewLayer:","\/\/   previewLayer.session = service.previewSession","","try await service.start()    \/\/ warm-up, restore enrolment, arm gate, start camera"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","text":"4. Enrol a face","anchor":"4-Enrol-a-face","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"enroll(name:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" runs a short guided capture, persists the gallery, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"re-arms the identity gate. Iterate the returned stream to coach the user:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["for await step in service.enroll(name: \"Alice\") {","    switch step.phase {","    case .capturing: show(step.prompt, progress: step.poseProgress)","    case .completed: dismiss()","    case .failed:    show(step.prompt)","    @unknown default: break","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"A single front pose is enough to separate the enrolled user from other","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"people. Pass ","type":"text"},{"code":"poses: PoseTarget.lightingAwareGallerySequence","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to also","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"capture off-axis poses + a lighting pass, which improves recall as the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"user turns their head.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"5. Run live recognition","anchor":"5-Run-live-recognition","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","code":["for await update in service.updates() {","    switch update.status {","    case .trusted:    badge(\"TRUSTED — \\(update.matchedName ?? \"\")\", .green)","    case .notTrusted: badge(\"NOT TRUSTED\", .red)","    case .badFraming: badge(\"ADJUST FRAMING\", .orange)","    case .noFace:     badge(\"NO FACE\", .gray)","    @unknown default: break","    }","    \/\/ update.livenessGenuine \/ update.depthIsThreeD are the contributing signals.","}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"update.status == .trusted","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" already fuses face recognition, liveness, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TrueDepth, with framing applied — you never pick a similarity threshold,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"and you never touch the identity gate (forgetting it would collapse trust","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to liveness + depth, so any live face would pass). The enrolled gallery is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"saved across launches automatically; ","type":"text"},{"code":"service.enrolledName","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" reflects who is","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"enrolled.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","text":"See also","anchor":"See-also","level":2},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A complete, runnable SwiftUI app lives in the package’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Examples\/FRPilot"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" — full API."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustUpdate","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" \/ "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/EnrollmentProgress","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" — the stream payloads."}]}]}]}]}],"references":{"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustUpdate":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"One per-frame trust readout, with the framing gate already applied — so the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consumer renders a state, not a fusion of raw signals. Yielded by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/updates()","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FaceTrustUpdate"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"FaceTrustUpdate"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"FaceTrustUpdate","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustUpdate","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustupdate"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"On-device face recognition with fused liveness and TrueDepth anti-spoofing."}],"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr","type":"topic","title":"YEOFR"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustService":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"FaceTrustService"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"FaceTrustService","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","title":"FaceTrustService","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustservice","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustService/updates()":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Per-frame trust verdicts for the recognition UI. Call once and iterate;"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the stream finishes on "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"stop()"},{"type":"text","text":". Newest-wins (the underlying camera"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"stream drops stale frames), so a slow consumer can’t back up memory."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"updates"},{"kind":"text","text":"() -> "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScS","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"AsyncStream"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR15FaceTrustUpdateV","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"FaceTrustUpdate"},{"kind":"text","text":">"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"updates()","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/updates()","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustservice\/updates()"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/FaceTrustService/enroll(name:poses:)":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Enrol "},{"code":"name","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" from the live camera and return a stream of capture"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"progress. The existing frame loop drives the gallery walk; on completion"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the service persists the gallery, refreshes "},{"code":"enrolledName","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", resets the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"trust pipeline against the fresh gallery, and re-arms the identity gate —"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the consumer does none of that."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"enroll"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"name"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"poses"},{"kind":"text","text":": ["},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR10PoseTargetO","text":"PoseTarget"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScS","text":"AsyncStream"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:5YEOFR18EnrollmentProgressV","text":"EnrollmentProgress"},{"kind":"text","text":">"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"enroll(name:poses:)","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/enroll(name:poses:)","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/facetrustservice\/enroll(name:poses:)"},"doc://com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR/documentation/YEOFR/EnrollmentProgress":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Progress for an in-flight enrolment capture. Yielded by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/FaceTrustService\/enroll(name:poses:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and the stream finishes once the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"gallery is banked (or the capture can’t start)."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"EnrollmentProgress"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"EnrollmentProgress","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","title":"EnrollmentProgress","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.youreyeonly.yeofr.YEOFR\/documentation\/YEOFR\/EnrollmentProgress","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/yeofr\/enrollmentprogress"}},"variantOverrides":[{"patch":[{"op":"replace","value":"occ","path":"\/identifier\/interfaceLanguage"},{"op":"add","value":null,"path":"\/topicSections"},{"op":"replace","value":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Getting-started","identifiers":[],"title":"Getting started"}],"path":"\/seeAlsoSections"}],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}]}